feature  windows  when  tbstyle  flat  used  create  flat  toolbar  for  some  reason  tbstyle  transparent  also  set  this  causes  the  toolbar  flicker  when  moved  resized  the  fix  clear  tbstyle  transparent  note  this  work  around  unnecessary  there  flickering  and  clearing  the  tbstyle  transparent  interferes  with  the  theme
feature  windows  despite  the  fact  that  the  tool  tip  text  contains  the  tooltip  will  not  honour  the  new  line  unless  ttm  setmaxtipwidth  set  the  fix  set  ttm  setmaxtipwidth  large  value
