bug  windows  despite  the  fact  that  the  image  list  index  has  never  been  set  for  the  item  windows  always  assumes  that  the  image  index  for  the  item  valid  when  item  inserted  the  image  index  zero  therefore  when  the  first  image  inserted  and  assigned  image  index  zero  every  item  draws  with  this  image  the  fix  set  the  image  index  none  when  the  item  created  this  not  necessary  the  case  when  the  item  has  the  btns  sep  style  because  separators  cannot  show  images
feature  windows  for  some  reason  tool  item  that  has  the  style  btns  sep  does  not  return  imagenone  when  queried  for  image  index  despite  the  fact  that  attempt  has  been  made  assign  image  the  item  result  operations  image  list  that  use  the  wrong  index  cause  random  results  the  fix  ensure  that  the  tool  item  not  separator  before  using  the  image  index  since  separators  cannot  have  image  and  one  never  assigned  this  not  problem
